Project Title: NodeJS Web Application Development

 Project Overview
   Objective: Develop a web application using NodeJS, ExpressJS, MongoDB, Mongoose, and EJS.

      1. Planning and Design (Day 1-2)
         - Define application requirements
         - Design database schema
         - Plan project structure
      2. Backend Development (Day 3-4)
         - Set up NodeJS and ExpressJS
         - Implement MongoDB and Mongoose for data storage
         - Create route and controller files
      3. Frontend Development (Day 5-6)
         - Integrate EJS templating
         - Implement UI design
         - Customize with CSS
      4. Testing (Day 7)
         - Unit testing for backend and frontend components
         - Integration testing
      5. Documentation and Deployment (Day 8)
         - Document code and functionality
         - Deploy the application
